<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "Profile Image" %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="col-md-7">
        <p>My name is Kanji Yomoda living in vancouver.  I am a growth hacker having a diverse set of skills, especially specializing SEO.  Now I put effort into learning back-end development through Ruby on Rails.  </p>

        <p>
        <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#jobHistory"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controls="jobHistory"
        >
          Job History
        </button>

          <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#education"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controls="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>

          <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#interview"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controls="interview"
          >
            Interview
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-3 ">
                  <%= image_tag("exidea-logo.jpg", height: '80', width: '80') %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-9 about-me-card">
                  <div><b>Web Director(Intern)</b><span style="color: #666"> / May 2016 â€“ Mar 2017<span></div>
                    I launched new web media from scratch. It became a media sell $80,000 per month after 6 months.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

           </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
             <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-3 ">
                <%= image_tag("agu-logo.jpg", height: '80', width: '80') %>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-9 about-me-card">
                Currently in Aoyama Gakuin University majoring in marketing.
              </div>
             </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="interview">
            <div class="card card-block">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-5">
                  <%= image_tag("https://01intern.com/magazine/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/a83be28929594f7522cbd850d8d298bb.jpg", height: '100', width: '150') %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-7 about-me-card">
                  Interviewed by recruitment agency.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card card-block">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-5">
                  <%= image_tag("http://exidea.co.jp/new/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/IMG_4485.jpg", height: '100', width: '150') %>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-7 about-me-card">
                  Interviewed by the company I worked at.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


